text: Bashmaki () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Alexandrovskoye Urban Settlement, Alexandrovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 34 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 21 km south- west from Alexandrovsk. == References == Category:Rural localities in Alexandrovsky District
title: Bashmaki
